{"tid":43969,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"堀北真希有母乳了","createTime":"2016-12-18T00:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T05:37:34.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a55595baf1c2ebf6a57bc0609e9f244bda83c55","tid":43969,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T00:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2016/12/18/1920705_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F1920705_1.jpg&h=12c95bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n28歲堀北真希與40歲老公山本耕史，傳出已於日前迎接第一胎誕生，成功晉升新手爸媽！夫婦倆雖尚未對外發表喜訊，但山本好友、天團「SMAP」香取慎吾昨在節目中，搶先一步對外公布好消息，在鏡頭前開心祝福好友當爸！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堀北肚中小寶貝原定明年1月誕生，新生命卻迫不及待早了一步來報到，昨香取登上節目《SmaSTATION！》，頂著9度低溫在戶外出外景，他表示：「雖然天氣很冷，但我有個溫暖的好消息要告訴大家，我的朋友山本耕史當爸了！山本、堀北夫妻恭喜你們！」開心獻上祝福。<br />\n<br />\n香取慎吾和山本耕史12年前因拍攝日劇《新撰組！》結為好友，香取昨雖未透露孩子性別、生日等細節，但看得出他相當替好友開心。而堀北先前也與經紀公司達成協議，日後將以照顧孩子為優先，工作以廣告代言為主，已有汽車、洗衣用品、保險等廣告廠商，準備捧上豐厚酬勞請她出馬代言。"},{"pid":"9130cfd79851664e2db639bd264cef61da7c9590","tid":43969,"uid":19624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3cd443f9cae495f8dd9f157fc94e20a711fa4f","tid":43969,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"撚有波咩佢"},{"pid":"0543af1aeafc83ea25b9ef282060838c75f43ef4","tid":43969,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/133652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F133652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0dd66e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n染到成頭金毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戶田依家正過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}